1.New value proposition on innovation developed, to be tested in 2022; 
2. Specific innovation experiments scaled-up - example is the behavioral experiment in electricity use; 
3. Data innovation - few pilots implemented on use of big data for development (with UNECE on estimation of the number of population, other).
